      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">26.604</ph> Policy.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Agencies shall encourage contractors and subcontractors to adopt and enforce policies that ban text messaging while driving-</p>
         <ol id="d1571e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1593e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Company-owned or rented vehicles or Government-owned vehicles; or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1593e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Privately-owned vehicles when on official Government business or when performing any work for or on behalf of the Government.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
